<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-83-0762 </DOCNO><TEXT>Considers electrical equipment on winning machines with regard to insulationand switching and equipment with micro-electronic components. Reviewsthe command and servo-control systems (programmable automatons in usein the large Hambach units). The introduction of fibre optic transmissionis also discussed. Describes the development of drive heads and 2000kW electric conveyor stations. Briefly comments on the Hambach electricrail network. 12 refs., 5 figs.</TEXT></DOC>